<br>
Head to Icewall Keep and kill Councilor Juliash Lockheart.  Now... she spawns the stadium lookin area (you'll see a sleeping guard in the bleachers), and winds up also heading up near the Dain when council is in session.  Make sure to kill her when she's in the stadium.  She's standing next to 2 other dorfs, but they dont assist.<br>
<br>
I killed her with a 62 Monk and 51 Shammy combo... cake kill.<br>
<br>
She DOES give a negative Coldain faction hit, but it's minor at best.<br>
<br>
The drop is usually (I got it 2 out of 3 kills) an Ornate Velium Pendant.  The item has 4 charges of &quot;Alliance&quot;.  Cast it and you have the instant faction needed to finish the turn ins for your epic.<br>
<br>
I've done this successfully, and can say from firsthand experience that it works just fine.<br>
<br>
I helped a fellow guildie as well who lost his oil to the Gnome in BB (he petitioned and got the oil back).  He used the necklace and did the oil turn in just fine (and the rest of his epic as well).<br>
<br>
It's a shame they bugged our quest so badly... but hopefully the above helps.<br>
<br>
